earch and underwriting methods to identify mispriced investment opportunities within the publicly listed real estate and infrastructure markets our investment approach includes topdown marketcountry selection and bottomup underwriting of properties companies and management teams in private equity real estate we focus on crafting unique options for repositioning special situation investments in middlemarket real estate across the us leadership team centersquare investment management is led by chief executive officer and chief investment officer e todd briddell with responsibility for overseeing the firm’s real asset investment advisory services including private equity real estate and listed real estate and infrastructure across the united states europe and asia centersquare’s private equity real estate group is led by david rabin and its listed real estate group is led by dean frankel and andrew nicholas global coheads of real estate securities centersquare’s listed infrastructure group is led by portfolio manager ted brooks centersquare has an extensive support team of portfolio managers and analysts to support this leadership team and assist in investment management decisions e todd briddell cfa chief executive officer chief investment officer centersquare scott crowe chief investment strategist centersquare frank j ferro general counsel centersquare joseph law chief financial officer chief compliance officer centersquare scott maguire cfa caia managing director global head of client service and marketing centersquare centersquare investment management holdings inc is a whollyowned subsidiary of the bank of new york mellon corporation centersquare investment management inc is a whollyowned subsidiary of centersquare investment management holdings inc  mark this link directs you to a thirdparty website dreyfus accepts no responsibility for content on these thirdparty sites or for the services provided also please be aware that when you use services provided by one 